data.title: News for the Monadnock Region
data.meta_description: Online edition of The Keene Sentinel - News in the Keene, NH area -  breaking news, local news, health, sports and much more
data.text:
Five Below in Keene is slated to open its doors in mid-September, according to a sign on the storefront in the Monadnock Marketplace.

Keene City Manager Elizabeth Dragon has promoted acting Fire Chief Jason Martin to the permanent position, which became official Sunday.

Cheshire County veterans can get free farmers market vouchers this September as part of an appreciation program for those who served.
